name: Envoy Blueprint Chip
desc: The Blueprint Chip for Envoy Initiatives is a specialized enhancement designed to optimize the operational capabilities of Envoy missions. This chip incorporates advanced technologies and methodologies to support various objectives, particularly in improving efficiency and effectiveness.

name: Envoy Blueprint Ship
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct ship hulls described by this blueprint.

name: Envoy Armory
desc: This collection features a series of armory blueprints that elevate civilian spacecraft, specifically Envoy models.
